import React from 'react'
import { Box, Text,Flex, Spacer, Container, Divider } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import Card from '../../../Components/Card/Card'
const DetailedBill = () => {
  return (
   <Card flexDirection="column" justify="flex-start" alignItems="flex-start">
     <Container>
     <Text>BILL DETAILS</Text>
     <Box mt="3%"  w="100%">
     <Flex w="100%">
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">Item Total</Text>
       <Spacer/>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">₹20</Text>
     </Flex>
     <Flex>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">Taxes & Charges</Text>
     <Spacer/>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">₹20</Text>
     </Flex> 
     <Flex>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">Tips</Text>
     <Spacer/>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">₹20</Text>
     </Flex>
     <Flex>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">Covenince charge</Text>
       <Spacer/>
       <Text lineHeight="22px" fontSize="13px">₹20</Text>
       </Flex> 
     </Box>
      <Divider mt="3%" mb="3%"/>
      <Flex>
       <Text lineHeight="30px" >To Pay</Text>
       <Spacer/>
       <Text lineHeight="30px" >₹80</Text>
       </Flex> 
     </Container>
   </Card>
  )
}

export default DetailedBill
